<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151095>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Rohdea brachyanthera. A. habit with flowering scape. B & C. Inflorescence. D & E. Flower, front view. F. Flower, side view. G. Portion of flower, longitudinal section. H, I & L. Portion of flower, longitudinal section and pistil has been removed. J. Portion of flower, lateral view. K. Top of flower, side view. M. Portion of top of flower, side view. top view. N & O. Ovary cross-section." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151095/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151097>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Rohdea fargesii var. tsinlingensis. A. Habit with flowering scape. B. Young inflorescence. C. Old inflorescence. D. Not fully opened flower, front view. E & F. Portion of not fully opened flower, longitudinal section. G. Flower, front view. H. Flower without pistil, front view and showing the interior. I. Flower in longitudinal section." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10151097/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151099>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Isotype of Rohdea watanabei. China, Taiwan, Xinzhu, E’gongjishan (Î»Θψ), K. Watanabe s.n. (TAIF 5998, image!)" ;
