<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10151101>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. R. watanabei in Hunan population.A. Habit. B. Inflorescence. C. Bracts. D. Flower, lateral view. E & F. Flower, vertical view. G & I. Flower, longitudinal section. H. Flower, vertical view and perianth tube had been cut open. Cultivated in nursery of Zaozhuang University, Shandong, China." ;
